Trigger Happy Elite v3.0 - GHOST PROTOCOL

is an ultra-aggressive, reversal-focused scalping strategy designed for high-frequency trades on volatile instruments like micro futures (MES, MNQ, MYM, etc.) during active sessions.

Core Logic:
• Entries trigger on ultra-sensitive 1-bar pivot highs/lows — pure "trigger happy" price action reversals.
• Optional "Ghost Reversals" (👻) mode: Catches stealth/failed pivots where a detected high/low fails to exceed the recent 50-bar extreme — often signaling liquidity grabs, traps, or hidden institutional reversals before the crowd notices.
• Dual filters ensure quality:
- RSI(14) must be in favorable territory (below Max RSI for buys, above Min RSI for sells).
- ATR(14) > Min Volatility threshold (default 2.2) — blocks entries in dead/choppy markets.

Risk & Reward Engine:
• Fixed targets: 250 ticks profit, 45 ticks hard stop (strong ~5.5:1 R:R on paper).
• Dynamic trailing stop: Activates after +20 ticks profit, then trails by user-defined offset (default 10 ticks) — locks in gains quickly while allowing some breathing room.
• Daily gates: Stops trading after hitting profit goal ($2000 default) or max drawdown (-$350 default).
• One position at a time — no pyramiding/overlapping.

Trading Window (optional):
• Restrict to RTH (e.g., 09:30–15:45 EST) or any custom session.

Alerts & Automation:
• Built-in JSON alert messages for easy webhook integration (buy/sell/close with ticker & price).
• Works best on 1–15 min charts of micro index futures during high-vol periods (open, news, power hours).

Important Notes:
• This is a high-trade-frequency scalper — expect many signals. Use on liquid micros with tight spreads.
• Backtest thoroughly — adjust pivot sensitivity (currently 1-bar), ghost lookback, ATR min, trail offset, etc., to match your symbol/timeframe.
• Risk management is built-in but NEVER risk more than 1–2% per trade in live accounts.
• Past performance ≠ future results. Trade at your own risk.

Inspired by structural reversal concepts and "missed reversal" / ghost logic seen in advanced SMC tools.

Happy scalping — stay trigger happy, but trade smart! 🎯👻

